Regular players can't flag an incorrect match — they have to contact an admin to void it. If the person entering matches (especially in admin mode) makes an error, there's no self-service remedy.

8. ~~Shadow profile name collisions~~ ✓ RESOLVED — findOrCreateShadowPlayer in lib/services/players.ts normalizes displayName (trim + collapse whitespace) and does a case-insensitive lookup before creating, preventing new duplicates. Existing duplicates in DB can be resolved via the admin merge tool.

