20. Privacy model: shadow profile consent
Shadow profiles (unclaimed players with userId IS NULL) have match history and ratings visible to all authenticated users. They never signed up or consented. At current scale this is a non-issue; at growth scale, especially with EU users, this may require action.
Options: (a) Show shadow profiles only to players who share at least one match; (b) Allow unclaiming/removal request via admin; (c) Explicit consent on claim flow.
No immediate action needed — revisit before any public launch or if app expands outside current community.

